{"tid":2089871,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張曉明稱「你做初一、我做十五」　美國出手必遭反制","createTime":"2020-07-02T01:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T01:01:06.000Z","uid":130626,"like":159,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":128,"replies":[{"pid":"b83f7d8e38917a2b63d636c1c80c838d496b5adf","tid":2089871,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:11:24.000Z","msg":"美國政府在《港區國安法》通過前，宣布部分制裁措施，包括限制中央官員的簽證，以及取消香港特殊待遇地位。在北京，港澳辦常務副主任張曉明在國新辦記者會上批評，美國有一些人的手伸得太長。<br />\n<br />\n張曉明警告，如果這種霸凌主義習性發作，覺得自己國家亂得不夠，不在乎所謂制裁造成的自身損失大於他人損失，想藉機轉嫁危機玩「甩鍋」，那就可以試試。他認為，這無非是給機會中方展示智慧還擊的能力。<br />\n<br />\n張曉明說，「你做初一、我做十五」，只要美國出手，中國政府和特區政府必定予以反制，有關措施會見步行步，陸續有來。<br />\n<br />\n他又認為，香港的特殊經濟地位，包括國際金融中心地位是長期形成，並且得到國際社會廣泛認同，獲得基本法保障，不是哪一國、哪一方予取予奪。<br />\n<br />\n張曉明說，對保障香港國際經濟地位不太擔心，因為香港的繁榮穩定取決於自身營商環境，以及內地經濟發展的勢頭，對香港的支持力度會否持續，他對此有信心。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535154-20200701.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535154-20200701.htm&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2B23B9TQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=ccfb3ee1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535154-20200701.htm&h=223f29da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535154-20200701.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b375c5166b643966a49ec9c83db657b5e278650e","tid":2089871,"uid":5475,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:12:40.000Z","msg":"下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊個係始作俑者先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b706a2f39acec3422486edf91f3e7e454903cc","tid":2089871,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c303bcef5b113f381b230c0a7e6d5adb77f0202","tid":2089871,"uid":6132,"like":221,"dislike":2,"score":219,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:13:42.000Z","msg":"好心佢咪再扮香港人講廣東話，好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e639f70de533062bcdd83683aaf5d5d535e7cf5","tid":2089871,"uid":2054,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:13:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他又認為，香港的特殊經濟地位，包括國際金融中心地位是長期形成，並且得到國際社會廣泛認同，獲得基本法保障，不是哪一國、哪一方予取予奪。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇吓點囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280311954df60bfdebe4c3fecfe3209f473ef7e6","tid":2089871,"uid":78515,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:14:13.000Z","msg":"並且得到國際社會廣泛認同<br />\n國際社會唔係美國咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3909d31994a2e21e274978d942f0af25c02a57ac","tid":2089871,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f25db81db03cce09ce70f5a529b3bdde0d539a","tid":2089871,"uid":19552,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:15:31.000Z","msg":"吹撚到香港靠支那發圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc37f9c85d711a32eed9c78dd1dbbd1013efc2c","tid":2089871,"uid":173060,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:15:38.000Z","msg":"呢條友其實係咪俾支那眨左去做華嬸同阿爽個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2bbc513a05f9aa61cf8fa288f4ba49e53e714e9","tid":2089871,"uid":322077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:15:56.000Z","msg":"加速師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40393714a8953c7220815ac17e61106fd55ce981","tid":2089871,"uid":89382,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"1c303bcef5b113f381b230c0a7e6d5adb77f0202","tid":2089871,"uid":6132,"like":221,"dislike":2,"score":219,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:13:42.000Z","msg":"好心佢咪再扮香港人講廣東話，好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:16:43.000Z","msg":"張屌明：支那人係duck既，生港係duck既"},{"pid":"92429f9fdb87cbc5f14dd5850dc566c363177465","tid":2089871,"uid":43197,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:20:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有關措施會見步行步</span></span><br />\n<br />\n即係無strategic  plan... <br />\n<br />\n自爆"},{"pid":"6e11ff47680d8ee2610f9eb667fbe3d0b10af91e","tid":2089871,"uid":522,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:21:48.000Z","msg":"香港人好撚慘, 成日比班大陸人騎劫發表戇鳩宣言"},{"pid":"c138fd27ffeecaedadb47e3af92244e79248c37c","tid":2089871,"uid":346701,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:22:06.000Z","msg":"聽佢講扮香港人講野就想打獲佢<br />\n死北佬仆街去死啦"},{"pid":"a6ef16a5027d9f14587c40c5bfc4b7fc74a97872","tid":2089871,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c303bcef5b113f381b230c0a7e6d5adb77f0202","tid":2089871,"uid":6132,"like":221,"dislike":2,"score":219,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:13:42.000Z","msg":"好心佢咪再扮香港人講廣東話，好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3dd3d6d589e64c7179d4f6fa110ba8bfa412c44","tid":2089871,"uid":50386,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:24:57.000Z","msg":"西方國家唔認同<br />\n唔通靠古巴沙特呢啲19國家認同就可以做金融中心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d570516d4d61057987e1a4476e9544981ab1d128","tid":2089871,"uid":274637,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:25:48.000Z","msg":"你做初一我做十五唔係指各有各做河水不犯井水咩。點解會變左反制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5004397a7cd4d7eb2c76be1591a27d96e000de3","tid":2089871,"uid":11291,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個十五幾時出嚟呀"},{"pid":"13768f2c714471dd793fc2ec75da22ab78db88cf","tid":2089871,"uid":86186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:26:21.000Z","msg":"你邊位呀"},{"pid":"7d5b33df63c5d297a0d6818aa4a19b6e2e62cb36","tid":2089871,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5004397a7cd4d7eb2c76be1591a27d96e000de3","tid":2089871,"uid":11291,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個十五幾時出嚟呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:27:00.000Z","msg":"口交部快啲啦唔好淨係識打飛機"},{"pid":"a02872d30da6d9bcb1a815570bee21dc432d2922","tid":2089871,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:27:00.000Z","msg":"一於派綠卡比美國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n借個位，BNO平權正視聽<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑色五毛分化警告，大量五毛正在用藍絲有BNO、走人對唔住97後割97後等風向進行分化</span></span></strong>，大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n1.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家比人拉過/有小朋友（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）的話就應該即刻走</span></span></strong>，其他人亦應該起碼做好隨時走既準備，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">香港抗爭運動已經由本土抗爭升級為準國際戰爭， 我們能做的十分有限。 相反大家離開或準備好隨時可以離開，則美國及其盟友可以隨時採取行動，對香港進行制裁，令香港達至零經濟活動，攬炒香港經濟， 甚至日後作出軍事行動亦無需擔心誤傷香港人。</span></span></strong> 而且大家亦可用移民理由提取所有資產及強積金進一步<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打擊香港的財政儲備</span></span></strong>。<br />\n而且多人走亦可以起到掩護最需要走既手足，救奶左野手足係目前最重要既事。<br />\n<br />\n2.大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無需擔心藍絲以及黑警移民英國</span></span></strong>，藍絲得兩種a.垃圾b.收成期，a.涯唔到六年移民監b.揾錢唔捨得走/走要承受巨大損失<br />\n<br />\n重點：大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不應該反對平權或推到現階段設立篩選，因為這樣會妨礙奶左野手足逃難</span></span></strong>。反而，大家應該在藍絲移民英國後再篤灰。大家，要記住，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">篤灰係一把藍絲頭上既利劍，一日未入籍一日都嚮度，我就係要佢地嚮英國每一日都擔心比人篤灰，呢樣恐懼做為懲罰先係最大懲罰</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">相反藍絲黑警，反而大家更應該想辦法推動取消侵犯人權者如689、777、鳩融居英權，因為他們可以一直不居英，不受英國審判，而定居歐洲。<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">97後手足唔會被割</span></span></strong>，首先，佢地可以跟BNO父母及配偶前往英國。第二，對於<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">未受BNO平權保障嘅人佢哋仲有美國既救生艇計劃</span></span></strong>，該計劃估計幾日內亦會通過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">希望樓主可以pin，一齊擊退五毛</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e7af5045c637fcc5b202a4ca84bda454c5a9eeab","tid":2089871,"uid":238301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:27:55.000Z","msg":"我反對你個反對"},{"pid":"7310b0fb26af0109bd2d249a3594b3b1f6687166","tid":2089871,"uid":221343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:28:23.000Z","msg":"邊個係初一邊個係十五都未搞清楚,成日衝出嚟柒,小明你返去進修下中文先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a883337957b3f238c9f1e97857c042de4cdb2b80","tid":2089871,"uid":74935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:28:35.000Z","msg":"唔講石頭腳啦？"},{"pid":"010fc298c89d8ba54a922a7bbc31d58a9446765f","tid":2089871,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:29:04.000Z","msg":"燉冬菇嘅芝麻狗官咁多嗲"},{"pid":"60e46276a034cc6e5f8682af0c28627052707056","tid":2089871,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:29:07.000Z","msg":"我做初一我做十五<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ebcb2bfa2208268515cc3901b831a75e2bc261","tid":2089871,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b83f7d8e38917a2b63d636c1c80c838d496b5adf","tid":2089871,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:11:24.000Z","msg":"美國政府在《港區國安法》通過前，宣布部分制裁措施，包括限制中央官員的簽證，以及取消香港特殊待遇地位。在北京，港澳辦常務副主任張曉明在國新辦記者會上批評，美國有一些人的手伸得太長。<br />\n<br />\n張曉明警告，如果這種霸凌主義習性發作，覺得自己國家亂得不夠，不在乎所謂制裁造成的自身損失大於他人損失，想藉機轉嫁危機玩「甩鍋」，那就可以試試。他認為，這無非是給機會中方展示智慧還擊的能力。<br />\n<br />\n張曉明說，「你做初一、我做十五」，只要美國出手，中國政府和特區政府必定予以反制，有關措施會見步行步，陸續有來。<br />\n<br />\n他又認為，香港的特殊經濟地位，包括國際金融中心地位是長期形成，並且得到國際社會廣泛認同，獲得基本法保障，不是哪一國、哪一方予取予奪。<br />\n<br />\n張曉明說，對保障香港國際經濟地位不太擔心，因為香港的繁榮穩定取決於自身營商環境，以及內地經濟發展的勢頭，對香港的支持力度會否持續，他對此有信心。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535154-20200701.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535154-20200701.htm&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2B23B9TQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=ccfb3ee1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535154-20200701.htm&h=223f29da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535154-20200701.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:29:15.000Z","msg":"淆底呀"},{"pid":"3292170802144de25c7f57e673c7351e085ce6e8","tid":2089871,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:29:47.000Z","msg":"明明比人燉冬菇 成日仲咁多嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6843e98945a0e238a5b694f541e723e2117834b2","tid":2089871,"uid":117679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"280311954df60bfdebe4c3fecfe3209f473ef7e6","tid":2089871,"uid":78515,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:14:13.000Z","msg":"並且得到國際社會廣泛認同<br />\n國際社會唔係美國咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:29:47.000Z","msg":"國際社會聲音不包括歐、美、澳、加、日。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a96ec5288dc3708c2b92ed22f8e49ec0eb5b6f5","tid":2089871,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:30:14.000Z","msg":"全力支持<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTurbo 加速"},{"pid":"aed515c110d19083247961631ab3a47c7c8f21c1","tid":2089871,"uid":78971,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"1c303bcef5b113f381b230c0a7e6d5adb77f0202","tid":2089871,"uid":6132,"like":221,"dislike":2,"score":219,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:13:42.000Z","msg":"好心佢咪再扮香港人講廣東話，好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:30:37.000Z","msg":"咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國人其中一個優點就係唔知醜"},{"pid":"29a28636396c9e241c1912cfb258fcc1e8766088","tid":2089871,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:31:46.000Z","msg":"推 香港自治法 全民舉報警渣有責<br />\n舉報熱線: <a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/contact/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fcontact%2F&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2B23B9TQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=c43a93c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/contact/</a><br />\n<br />\n金融戰線 BNO準備開通<br />\n永久離港 和你提清MPF"},{"pid":"7330ee615a672665448286885c44a433bdc558ae","tid":2089871,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"